# SEO & PWA Optimization – Best Practice 2025

## Principi

- Meta tag SEO completi (title, description, og, twitter)
- Structured data JSON-LD
- Manifest PWA e service worker
- Sitemap.xml e robots.txt
- Mobile SEO: font ≥16px, tap target ≥44px
- Lighthouse: accessibilità ≥95, performance ≥90

## Esempi chiave

### Meta Tag

```html
<meta name="description" content="Portfolio Alice Mandelli – Web Designer UI 2025" />
<meta property="og:title" content="Alice Mandelli – Web Designer" />
```

